description: A black and white photo looking down on a curb stop (aka parking block) at the end of a parking space. The concrete block is in the upper third of the image extending out from the left side of the image most of the way to the right side of the frame. The block is on black asphalt which takes up the top half of the frame. The lower half of the frame is white sidewalk. The side walk has a thin, vertical expansion slot close to the left side and a thicker horizontal one that's above the lower edge of the frame at the same distance the vertical one is from the left. Two dark shadows extend from the left side of the image diagonally towards the right. The top shadow begins on the right side of the top edge. The second shadow starts a third of the way down on the left side.
